title: This Life of Fulfillment May be Yours Through the Power Teach
description: Illustration and two letters. Illustration of a man wearing academic regalia and bearing a scroll labeled 'TRUTH.' He is walking out of a building labeled 'KNOWLEDGE OF THE LIVING GOD' and down a path labeled 'LIFE OF FULFILLMENT' toward a rising sun. The letter under the illustration discusses the way God is available for all persons. The reverse side contains a letter titled 'A WORD OF WARNING' that states that, although there are wondrous benefits to tapping the God-Power, the knowledge also comes with the responsibility to recruit others to the Psychiana cause.
